{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_haini_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_haini_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"怀有希望之人","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"卢契拉与深海教徒的联系使她成为海巡队的严密监视对象，但她后续的行动出乎所有人的意料。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_haini_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["海巡队队长","卢契拉","安妮娅","帕波斯","海巡队队员"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"各组注意，卢契拉正在协助深海教徒逃跑。","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"卢契拉需要被当作新的嫌疑人进行追踪。","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"她的举动足以证明——她有背叛阿戈尔的意图。","id":13},{"type":"dialog","id":14},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":15},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"charslot","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":18},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dd/Avg_bg_bg_light.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":19},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":20,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":22},{"type":"text","text":"十二小时前，海巡队办公室","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"你说安妮娅“企图”把占领了火山能源站的海嗣引到城市来？噗，什么恶劣的玩笑，还管她叫深海教徒。","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"这里不是开玩笑的地方。失窃的海嗣诱导信息素，出海时间，一切线索都指向安妮娅和她的导师。希望你配合我们的调查。","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我们的城市是为了躲避海嗣才开始移动的不是吗？安妮娅居然会把没追上我们的海嗣再引过来？呵，她为什么要这样做？","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"安妮娅现在怎么样了？她在哪儿？","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"她的生命体征已于事发时消失。","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"安妮娅她......死了？","id":29},{"type":"dialog","id":30},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":31},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":32},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":33},{"type":"charslot","id":34},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":35},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":36},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_calm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":37,"musicid":1},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":38},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":39},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":40},{"type":"text","text":"坐在透明的穹顶夹层里，静静欣赏穹顶外的景色时，会让人产生错觉，仿佛自己正漂浮在海洋中央，被澄澈的海水包围。","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安妮娅","text":"呼——头有些晕。","id":42},{"type":"dialog","id":43},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":44},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":45},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"来一点神经稳定剂？对恐高引起的眩晕感有抑制作用——特地给你准备的。怕苦的话还有这个——","id":47},{"type":"dialog","id":48},{"type":"text","text":"卢契拉从口袋里华丽地“变”出了一支甜味剂，安妮娅笑了笑。","id":49},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我今天早上听说，你的生物探测装置又被海嗣破坏了，就猜到你完事了之后会过来。","id":51},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安妮娅","text":"嗯。去重装的时候遇到海嗣了，零星几只。","id":53},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"又......这次有多近？","id":55},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"none","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安妮娅","text":"......","id":57},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"这半年来，是不是越来越频繁了？我感觉你每次来的时候，总是很疲惫......","id":59},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","focus":"none","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安妮娅","text":"......","id":61},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"睡着了？","id":63},{"type":"dialog","id":64},{"type":"charslot","id":65},{"type":"text","text":"卢契拉侧过头看了看。安妮娅把头靠在她的肩上，正静静地欣赏着穹顶外澄澈的海洋。","id":66},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"安妮娅......和我说说，外海真的那么恐怖吗？","id":68},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我......我每天在最贴近海洋的地方工作，却从未看见过它们。","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我能看见的，只有不断出海的军队，还有你和你的导师，每天为了恢复大洋生态而努力。","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我有时候会想......一线的战场究竟是什么样的？我从穹顶看到的安宁，究竟是你们用什么换来的......","id":72},{"type":"dialog","id":73},{"type":"charslot","id":74},{"type":"text","text":"安妮娅低声说着什么，卢契拉忍不住侧过头看着她的眼睛。","id":75},{"type":"dialog","id":76},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":77},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":78},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"charslot","id":80},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":81},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":82},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":83},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":84,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":86},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":87},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","duration":"1.5","id":88},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":89},{"type":"text","text":"卢契拉走出海巡队办公室时，仍然没有回过神。她无助地一遍遍联系安妮娅，却始终没有回应。","id":90},{"type":"dialog","id":91},{"type":"playsound","key":"$phone","volume":"1","channel":"1","id":92},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"这是......？！","id":94},{"type":"dialog","id":95},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"1","id":96},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":97},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":98},{"type":"sticker","id":99,"multi":"true","text":"卢契拉，","x":"300","y":"250","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":100,"multi":"true","text":"\\n\\n\\n想必你也受到了海巡队的调查，他们会告诉你，安妮娅试图引导能源站的海嗣来追击我们撤退中的城市。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":101,"multi":"true","text":"\\n关于安妮娅的真实死因，我有重要的事实相告。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":102},{"type":"sticker","id":103,"multi":"true","text":"看在她的分上，收到信息后请马上与我见一面。","x":"300","y":"300","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":104,"multi":"true","text":"\\n作为她的友人，你不会置之不理，对吗？","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":105,"multi":"true","text":"\\n\\n\\n帕波斯","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":106},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"（安妮娅的导师......事发那天和她在一起的人！）","id":109},{"type":"dialog","id":110},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":111},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"charslot","id":114},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":115},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":116},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":117,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":118},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":119},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":120},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","duration":"1.5","id":121},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":122},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":123},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"呼——呼——","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"甩掉了吗，那些海巡队的家伙？","id":126},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"咳......已经看不见他们的制服了......","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"你可真是......我只是说，他们在跟踪我，你怎么就跑起来了......你就不怕海巡队把你当成我的共犯吗？","id":129},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我要知道真相，在那之前谁也别想抓走您。","id":131},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"告诉我，安妮娅她真的已经......？","id":133},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"牺牲了，是的。","id":135},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我们约好一起去看展，她突然爽约，就是为了跟您出海。到底发生了什么？您被海巡队跟踪的事和她有关吗？","id":138},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"他们怀疑我是深海教徒，但是无法证明。","id":140},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"您是吗？","id":142},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"我不喜欢这个称呼。我不信仰任何教义，我只坚信我坚信的。","id":144},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......所以，“是”。安妮娅......呢？","id":146},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"安妮娅——是我最好的学生，无论是在学术方面，还是在对海嗣的态度上。她什么都没和你提过吗？","id":148},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":150},{"type":"dialog","id":151},{"type":"charslot","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"他们不跑了。保持距离，让他们以为摆脱了跟踪。","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"帕波斯接触的这名女性的身份查到了——技术院设施管理所的穹顶维护员卢契拉。","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"我知道她。不久前我们对她进行了调查，她说就算自己堕落了，安妮娅都不会堕落。","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"调取距离最近的摄像头，听听他们在说什么。","id":156},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":158},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"您在说谎。您说您要告诉我真相，可您和海巡队说得一样——","id":160},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"“她是深海教徒，她引导海嗣追击城市。”好像她的死亡毫不意外，罪有应得。","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"这有什么不一样？这算哪门子的真相？","id":163},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"卢契拉，你需要冷静下来，别这么大声。","id":165},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我很冷静。在这件荒谬的事里我是最冷静的！","id":167},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"我来找你，是需要你完成她真正的愿望。只有你可以做到。","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"我要你把我藏在礁石里的安妮娅的遗体运回城市里。看到她的遗体，你将明白一切。","id":170},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"她的......遗体？","id":172},{"type":"dialog","id":173},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"charslot","id":176},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":177},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":178},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":180},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":181},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","duration":"1.5","id":182},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":183},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":184},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"好了，在这里谈话更安全。","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"我知道挚友突然被称呼为“遗体”，对你来说冲击很大。但你必须了解她生前为实现愿望作出了何等壮烈的牺牲。","id":187},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"您是说这一切是她自己的选择？","id":189},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"我和安妮娅得出的结论是经过了无数次的辩驳和论证的。人类本就是食物链的一环，不想沦为海洋生态圈的底端，只有进化。","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"而进化的顶点——海嗣，向我们敞开大门。","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"为了所谓的人类尊严而拒绝加入进化的行列，难道不是一种傲慢，不是对人类种群的不负责任吗？难道——","id":193},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"停。什么进化，什么傲慢，我听不懂你在说什么......","id":195},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"唉......我理解你的怀疑。的确，安妮娅一开始也像你一样反感我的提议。","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"但你已经知道事实了，她最后甚至夺过我手中的信息素，亲手引导海嗣。","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"如果承担的是整个人类的命运，就需要有相应的认知——对即将承受的痛苦、道德的谴责。你认识的安妮娅不是这样的人吗？","id":199},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":200},{"type":"text","text":"卢契拉瞪着眼前的老者。她想否认她所听到的，而所有的事实又在拉扯她的内心。","id":201},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......您还是没有说，遗体是怎么回事。","id":203},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"在她离开前，她承诺就算计划没有成功，也会带回海嗣的活体细胞。","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"我最后拼尽全力，回收了她残留的一只手。那只手还紧紧攥着她承诺过的东西。","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"我没法从正常渠道把它带进来，你知道的。穹顶上有清洁机器人的出入口，那个大小正好。","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"只要作为穹顶维护员的你施展一些小手段，骗过他们的监管......","id":208},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"安妮娅的愿望......","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":211},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"如果，这真的是她的愿望......只要把她带回家，就好了，对吗？","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"告诉我，藏着她的......遗体的礁石在哪儿。","id":214},{"type":"dialog","id":215},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":217},{"type":"charslot","id":218},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":219},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":220},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":221},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":222},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"（能源站附近的礁石群里，藏着安妮娅和她的愿望......）","id":224},{"type":"dialog","id":225},{"type":"charslot","id":226},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":227},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":228},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":229},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":230},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"需要做好心理准备，卢契拉。距离事发已经过去二十四小时，你朋友的遗体将面目全非。","id":232},{"type":"dialog","id":233},{"type":"charslot","id":234},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"没关系，我只是想亲眼见证——她最后的愿望。","id":236},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"你在接受调查的过程中提到过，自己也曾有过堕落的想法。但你决定向我们举报帕波斯，你做出了正确的选择。","id":238},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我只是觉得，让海嗣来追击城市这种事，不像是她的愿望。","id":240},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"尽管你这么说，我仍希望你再考虑一下我们的提议。帕波斯现在已经躲藏起来了，由你把他约出来，能够提高我们的效率。","id":242},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我......","id":244},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"在标记范围内找到了一只人类的手，现在请技术员做分析。","id":246},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"！","id":248},{"type":"dialog","id":249},{"type":"charslot","id":250},{"type":"text","text":"海巡队队员递来一个透明的器皿，里面装着被泡得发白肿胀的肢体。","id":251},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":253},{"type":"dialog","id":254},{"type":"text","text":"卢契拉盯着那只手一动不动。","id":255},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"你还好吗？","id":257},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":258},{"type":"text","text":"不好。脑袋像炸裂了一样，屏蔽了所有的理性。卢契拉僵硬地站了好一会儿，才能发出声音。","id":259},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"这的确是她的手......我们总是盯着同一块操作面板，她在上面比划来比划去......我认得她的指甲。","id":261},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"她手里攥着的是什么？","id":263},{"type":"dialog","id":264},{"type":"charslot","id":265},{"type":"text","text":"在技术员谨慎的处理下，一个用于存储液体的小型密封罐被取了下来。","id":266},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"（这是......！）","id":268},{"type":"dialog","id":269},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":270},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"（原来是这样。我明白了——被你紧紧攥着的这只密封罐，这就是你的愿望，安妮娅。）","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......你知道吗，我刚刚决定了。我可以帮你们，帮你们把帕波斯约出来。","id":273},{"type":"dialog","id":274},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":275},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":276},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"charslot","id":278},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":279},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_suspenseful_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":280,"musicid":4},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":281},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":282},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":283},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":284},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","duration":"1.5","id":285},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":286},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","id":287},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"none","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"卢契拉，距离会面还有五分钟，帕波斯随时会出现。你需要靠近建筑物一点。你越走越偏了，出事的话我们很难及时赶到。","id":289},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":291},{"type":"dialog","id":292},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":293},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"100,0","duration":"1.5","id":294},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":295},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":296},{"type":"charslot","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"卢契拉？","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"没有回应。各组，做好卢契拉不配合的准备。","id":299},{"type":"dialog","id":300},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":301},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":302},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"——","id":304},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"帕波斯出现。","id":306},{"type":"dialog","id":307},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":308},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","posfrom":"300,0","posto":"100,0","duration":"1.5","id":309},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"1","id":310},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":311},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"跟我来，快。海巡队已经知道我们的计划了。我要帮您逃走。","id":313},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"什么？我需要更详细的解释......","id":315},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"来不及了，跑起来！","id":317},{"type":"dialog","id":318},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":319},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"1.5","id":320},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":321},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-100,0","duration":"1.5","id":322},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":323},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":324},{"type":"charslot","id":325},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":326},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"果然担心不是多余的。","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"各组注意，卢契拉正在协助深海教徒逃跑。","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"卢契拉需要被当作新的嫌疑人进行追踪。","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"她的举动足以证明——她有背叛阿戈尔的意图。","id":331},{"type":"dialog","id":332},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":334},{"type":"charslot","id":335},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":336},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":337},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":338},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":339},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":340},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":341},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","duration":"1.5","id":342},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":343},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"这里是......城市水循环系统？","id":345},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"城市入水管道和穹顶是相连的，也在我的管辖范围内。我权限内能锁的门都锁了，他们追上来还需要一段时间。","id":347},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"这和我们说好的不一样，卢契拉。","id":349},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"城市在移动中，他们对穹顶的监视比平时更严密，只有城市入水口还不在他们的监视范围内。只是需要人钻进管道里把东西截获。","id":351},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"稍等，让我想想。","id":353},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"怎么，在担心风险吗？作为她最敬仰的老师，您的勇气不会弱于安妮娅吧？","id":355},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"不。事情突然变成这样，我还能完全相信你吗，卢契拉？","id":357},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我们不需要信任彼此。您要您的东西，我为安妮娅完成最后的愿望，仅此而已。","id":359},{"type":"dialog","id":360},{"type":"charslot","id":361},{"type":"text","text":"帕波斯注视着卢契拉的双眼，思考了片刻。","id":362},{"type":"text","text":"如果要出卖他的话，卢契拉不会多此一举地带他逃跑。没有人会做这样效率低下的事。他松了口气。","id":363},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":364},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"昨天见面的时候，你的眼里满是犹豫，而现在你眼里的迷雾已经散去了。看来你做出了选择，这很好。","id":366},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"那抓紧时间，您现在就需要进入管道。","id":368},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"现在......？我没有穿任何防护装备。","id":370},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"您在说什么？安妮娅毫不犹豫地夺过了您手里的诱导信息素，而您却在担心这些小事？","id":372},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"快，我已经打开了加料口，维持不了太久，快进去！","id":374},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"这里面是......！","id":376},{"type":"dialog","id":377},{"type":"charslot","id":378},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punch","id":379},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"10","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":380},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":381},{"type":"text","text":"帕波斯发现不对劲的时候，感到后背被推了一下，径直跌入了管道中。","id":382},{"type":"text","text":"卢契拉随后关闭了污水处理的加料口。她瞪着空气，抓着把手的手在微微颤抖。","id":383},{"type":"text","text":"但是过了一会儿，她回过神，幸灾乐祸地笑了一声。","id":384},{"type":"dialog","id":385},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":386},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":387},{"type":"charslot","id":388},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_jump_water","id":389},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":390},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":391},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":392},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":393,"musicid":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":394},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":395},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":396},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","duration":"1.5","id":397},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":398},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","id":399},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"none","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"唔！这可怕的气味！这，呃，包围我的，难道不是污水吗！","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"卢契拉，你在那里吗？","id":402},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"你找到东西了吗？","id":404},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"none","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"这里的水流太激烈了！管壁很滑，我被......被冲得无法保持平衡！啊......！","id":406},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"你可得忍忍，在水里多摸摸。这是为了整个城市的未来啊。","id":408},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"none","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"城市入水口的管道里怎么会是污水？唔！呸！哕......","id":410},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"哈，我忘了告诉你吗，这里是城市的内循环管道，处理藻类发酵残留物用的。城市入水口这么重要的管道，怎么会让你说进就进。","id":412},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"卢契拉，你在戏弄我......你为什么......呕！呃......咳咳咳！","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"......打开，放我出去。","id":415},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"和我说说安妮娅，帕波斯。她最后是怎么对你说的？","id":417},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"none","id":418},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"呃......咳咳！这里的空气让我无法呼吸......","id":419},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"回答我，或者我们也可以继续耗着。","id":421},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"none","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"我已经把该告诉你的都告诉你了。","id":423},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":425},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"none","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"好吧，如果你一定要听......唔，咳咳！海嗣攻占能源站后，我意识到这是我唯一的机会——要趁城市还没有撤离得太远，把海嗣引过来。","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"我到达了能源站附近，却发现安妮娅也赶了过来。匆忙出海导致她驾驶舱的能源没来得及充满——这是我后来才发现的。","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"我们离能源站很近，已经有海嗣发现了我们......我们没时间交流了，至少要成功地释放信息素，把它们引向城市——","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"于是安妮娅抢走我手里的信息素，承诺她会完成任务，让我马上回到城市，我就进入了驾驶舱——总得有人完成后备计划。","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"可是她的驾驶舱动力不足，被海嗣拖住。最后我从驾驶舱的通讯里听到她一直在说，说她会抓牢的。咳咳咳！呕——","id":431},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"抓牢什么？","id":433},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"none","id":434},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"海嗣活体样本，只能是这个。因为我向她提起过我的后备计划，尽管曾经我们颇有争执，但到了那一刻，我们心照不宣。","id":435},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"她的遗体，我已经拜托海巡队找到了。","id":437},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"none","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"......你向海巡队告了密？卢契拉你......真的懂安妮娅吗？","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"呵，是啊，你总是躲在看不见海嗣的穹顶，望着那片纯净的水域，你又怎么会理解她的感受，我的感受。","id":440},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我看到了她手心里的东西，她即使被海嗣分食也要“抓牢”的东西。","id":442},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"none","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"你把安妮娅拼命留下来的——","id":444},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"是一支从未打开过的诱导信息素，帕波斯。","id":446},{"type":"dialog","id":447},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":448},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":449},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":450},{"type":"charslot","id":451},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":452},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":453},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":454,"musicid":6},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":455},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":456},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":457},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"安妮娅......和我说说，外海真的那么恐怖吗？","id":459},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我......我每天在最贴近海洋的地方工作，却从未看见过它们。","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我能看见的，只有不断出海的军队，还有你和你的导师，每天为了恢复大洋生态而努力。","id":462},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我有时候会想......一线的战场究竟是什么样的？我从穹顶看到的安宁，究竟是你们用什么换来的......","id":463},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"none","id":464},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安妮娅","text":"傻瓜。","id":465},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"哈？","id":467},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"none","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安妮娅","text":"你不需要知道。你不知道——才是最好的。","id":469},{"type":"dialog","id":470},{"type":"charslot","id":471},{"type":"text","text":"安妮娅的眼睛微微睁大，抬起手来。卢契拉顺着她手指的方向望向海洋，忍不住屏住呼吸。","id":472},{"type":"text","text":"此时正值火山的岩浆从城市底下爬上海床，呈辐射状一路映亮了海床上的礁石与生物。这样的景色无论看几次，卢契拉都不会厌倦。","id":473},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"none","id":474},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安妮娅","text":"海底的夕照。真幸运！来晚了可就看不到了。","id":475},{"type":"dialog","id":476},{"type":"charslot","id":477},{"type":"text","text":"卢契拉忍不住侧过头看着她的眼睛。安妮娅喜悦的眼睛里映出了她们深爱的海洋，阿戈尔人的家。","id":478},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"“怀有希望之人”——我脑子里突然蹦出这么几个字。对了，这是最近一场美术展的名字，什么时候的展来着......","id":480},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":481},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......啊，就在两天后！","id":482},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#5$1","focus":"none","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安妮娅","text":"那后天工作后的安排不就有了？我们去欣赏欣赏那些“怀有希望之人”的创作，怎么样？","id":484},{"type":"dialog","id":485},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":486},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":487},{"type":"charslot","id":488},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":489},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":490},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":491},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":492},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":493},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":494},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我就知道，她从始至终没有放开过诱导信息素，没有让它把海嗣引向城市。","id":495},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"而你......愚蠢的、懦弱的你......","id":496},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"none","id":497},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"......卢契拉，你知道弥利亚留姆明明能够抵御这批海嗣，为什么却要撤走吗？","id":498},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"弥利亚留姆——它不是撤走，是向着陆地去了。阿戈尔还在做无用的挣扎......","id":499},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":500},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"你又来了，我真的听不懂你在说什么！","id":501},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"听起来就好像遇到海嗣想逃跑，就叫无用的挣扎，与海嗣拼完命想回来看看澄澈的海，也是无用的挣扎。","id":502},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":503},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"那安妮娅救你的举动，在你眼里，也是无用的挣扎？！哈，那我可真是做对了！","id":504},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#7$1","focus":"none","id":505},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"收手吧。你就算把我淹死在这里，也证明不了对错，更无益于未来......","id":506},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":507},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":508},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"none","id":509},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"你......真的打算这样做吗，卢契拉......？","id":510},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":511},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":512},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"none","id":513},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"好，如果这是你认定的未来——","id":514},{"type":"dialog","id":515},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","id":516},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":517},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":518},{"type":"text","text":"愤怒的挂断声将帕波斯的声音切断。","id":519},{"type":"dialog","id":520},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":521},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":522},{"type":"charslot","id":523},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":524},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":525},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":526},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":527},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":528},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":529},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":530},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":531},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":532},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"在城市内循环入口发现卢契拉。没有发现帕波斯的行踪。","id":533},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":534},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"二组三组搜索帕波斯的行踪。一组跟我上！","id":535},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"卢契拉，不要动。","id":536},{"type":"dialog","id":537},{"type":"charslot","id":538},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":539},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我还是第一次被这样指着呢。","id":540},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":541},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"帕波斯在哪里？","id":542},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":543},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我可不知道，我又不是公共养育所所长，丢了人还要问我吗。","id":544},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":545},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"他有重要的线索，还不能死。他在管道里对吗？在哪个位置？","id":546},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":547},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"海巡队还真是自说自话，不听人解释呢。","id":548},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":549},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"你的眼里有愤怒。我处理过多次这样的事件，受害者的亲友眼里，都有这样无从纾解的愤怒。","id":550},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":551},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":552},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":553},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"你的时间不多了。从你们进入这里到现在，已经过去了五分钟。如果他真的在管道的某处，现在已经到达生理极限了。","id":554},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":555},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"呵，溺死在废水管道里，不觉得是与他特别相称的死法吗？","id":556},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":557},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"说出他的位置，马上。","id":558},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":559},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"——","id":560},{"type":"dialog","id":561},{"type":"charslot","id":562},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":563},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":564},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":565},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":566},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"找到嫌疑人帕波斯了！正在通知急救机器人过来！","id":567},{"type":"dialog","id":568},{"type":"charslot","id":569},{"type":"text","text":"远处，浑身散发着恶臭的帕波斯直直地躺在地上，面色惨白，一动不动。","id":570},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":571},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":572},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"我看看。他......","id":573},{"type":"dialog","id":574},{"type":"charslot","id":575},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕波斯","text":"咳......","id":576},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":577},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":578},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"还活着——","id":579},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":580},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"幸好这里的管道口开着，有新鲜空气流入。我们发现他的时候他几乎要失去意识，但还在试着往上爬。","id":581},{"type":"dialog","id":582},{"type":"charslot","id":583},{"type":"text","text":"听到管道口是开着的，海巡队队长意识到了什么，望向卢契拉，后者自嘲地笑了起来，笑着笑着，眼泪浸湿了眼眶。","id":584},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":585},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"真奇怪，原来我做不到。我没办法毁掉她最后的愿望，付出生命也要拯救的人......便宜他了。","id":586},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1390_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":587},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队长","text":"你做了正确的选择，再一次。我希望这一次你的选择发自内心。","id":588},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":589},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"放心吧......你们没有堕落的穹顶维护员需要处决。","id":590},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":591},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"至于给海巡队带来了这么多麻烦，我接受处理。只是你们可要抓紧时间，我还有一场展览要看。","id":592},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":593},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"虽然陪我去的人不在了，但我答应过她，去看看那些人——看看他们所怀有的希望。","id":594},{"type":"dialog","id":595},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":596},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":597},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":598},{"type":"text","text":"卢契拉向海巡队的舰艇走去，然而神色却比来时释然，脚步也更轻快。她低头看看自己的手，好像与那只熟悉的手又握在了一起。","id":599},{"type":"dialog","id":600},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":601},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":602},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":603},{"type":"charslot","id":604},{"type":"image","id":605}],"characters":["海巡队队长","卢契拉","安妮娅","帕波斯","海巡队队员"]}